title: LIBERALISM AFTER TRUMP With Ian Dunt
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: Ian Dunt returns to the podcast for a pig picture talk on liberalism - What is it's future after trump, how does/should the ideology manage conflict, what are the differences between the UK and US left? We cover a lot and end on an uncharacteristically (for us) optimistic note.
